      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Well-kept used car in good condition. It starts, runs, and drives well, and overall it has been cared for better than average. Expect a clean, presentable interior and exterior with normal signs of use for its age, but no major red flags suggested by its condition. A buyer should expect a solid, dependable used vehicle that may still have the routine wear and maintenance needs that come with any pre-owned car.",
