    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle that offers an accessible path to ownership without a big upfront investment. This car shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer, daily commuter on a budget, or someone looking for a solid project opportunity. Offered with straightforward pricing and honest presentation, it delivers affordable transportation potential at a compelling price point.",
