      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Honest, tough, and full of possibility, this car has the kind of road-worn character you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s the sort of ride that feels right at home in the hands of someone who sees potential where others just see age\u2014a perfect canvas for a budget-friendly commuter, weekend project, or dependable backup with plenty of story left to tell. If you want something polished, keep scrolling. If you want something affordable with personality and purpose, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
