      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an approachable price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability, practicality, and the chance to put their own touch on it. A straightforward option for commuting, a first car, or a project-minded owner looking for solid value.",
