    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants dependable budget transportation, a handy runaround, or a project to make their own. Honest car at an honest price, and a great way to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re after value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 3900.0,
