      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who wants an affordable driver/project with good bones. This car presents in poor cosmetic condition, but it still offers a responsive drivetrain, well-sorted chassis feel, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it appealing to an enthusiast or hands-on owner. Starts, runs, and delivers the raw, analog character people look for in an older used car, with plenty of upside for someone willing to put in some cosmetic and deferred-maintenance work. Priced to reflect condition while still giving you a capable platform to improve and enjoy.",
